喺將軍澳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你想出夜街?<br />\n肯定要call uber / 的士先返到屋企<br />\n因為地鐵收咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2012年入伙話起商場/海濱長廊<br />\n起撚到而家都未有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n落雨你以為有瓦遮頭呀?<br />\n有同冇都冇分別，大風到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n塊地板物料仲要冼腳嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結論: 退休人士入去住就冇所謂<br />\n我就死都唔入去住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9512689bbbbf1a2577d428f43277c252d6fe91be","tid":1078641,"uid":164218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"439ddb59ac4512ad48d8e0826f94fbe0b59374f7","tid":1078641,"uid":186854,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"b99892ada2fdb03b5f78a1e516b21558e5d89249","tid":1078641,"uid":164218,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5664a5bdb35168794037b36534c745d405ef0cde","tid":1078641,"uid":186854,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T02:25:55.000Z","msg":"其實你有無入去實地行下"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T02:38:09.000Z","msg":"我當然有，你想講乜咪直講lor"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T03:00:30.000Z","msg":"只係我行咗一次，遠撚到癲。十幾分鐘"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T03:22:14.000Z","msg":"而家在c 出口去4 期or 5 期就算兜路都大概係12-13mins, <br />\n開左b 出口再經商場and 天橋都幾肯定會縮減到7-8mins 內，話10 mins 都太過保守了"},{"pid":"ea05210d037020ce6afda83409db38dcb908a347","tid":1078641,"uid":231110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b99892ada2fdb03b5f78a1e516b21558e5d89249","tid":1078641,"uid":164218,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5664a5bdb35168794037b36534c745d405ef0cde","tid":1078641,"uid":186854,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d62df28b8b275acb445ed8f75c51556887fb45ac","tid":1078641,"uid":164218,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T02:22:03.000Z","msg":"商場下年開張，到時各期都係用5-10mins 就會到